#for k'8s cluster we need (minimal) 1 master and 2 slave nodes.

#setting up the master#
use any linux distribution with 2core(ubuntu/redhat/centos)
1st:ETCD server(cluster store)
2nd.API server(port443)
3rd. Schedular
4.Control Manager

